statements: SELECT * FROM network_operations;
SELECT operation_name, operation_type, status FROM network_operations WHERE ai_model_id = 1;
SELECT operation_id, operation_name, start_time, end_time FROM network_operations WHERE status = 'completed';
SELECT * FROM network_operations WHERE operation_type = 'classification' ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT operation_id, operation_name FROM network_operations WHERE end_time IS NULL ORDER BY operation_id ASC;
SELECT operation_id, operation_name, operation_type FROM network_operations WHERE status = 'completed';
SELECT * FROM network_operations ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT operation_id, operation_name, status FROM network_operations WHERE start_time > '2021-01-01' AND operation_type = 'classification' ORDER BY operation_id ASC;
SELECT operation_id, operation_name, end_time FROM network_operations WHERE status = 'pending' OR status = 'in-progress';
SELECT operation_id, ai_model_id, DATEDIFF(end_time, start_time) AS duration FROM network_operations WHERE status = 'completed' AND DATEDIFF(end_time, start_time) > 5 ORDER BY duration DESC;
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems;
SELECT system_name, integration_type FROM AI_Systems;
SELECT system_name, integration_type, managed_operations FROM AI_Systems WHERE managed_operations = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM Network_Operations WHERE operation_status = FALSE;
SELECT operation_id, operation_description FROM Network_Operations ORDER BY operation_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems WHERE managed_operations = TRUE;
SELECT system_name, integration_type FROM AI_Systems ORDER BY system_name ASC;
SELECT operation_id, operation_description, operation_status FROM Network_Operations WHERE ai_system_id = 1;
SELECT system_name, integration_type, managed_operations FROM AI_Systems WHERE integration_type = 'API';
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems JOIN Network_Operations ON AI_Systems.id = Network_Operations.ai_system_id;
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems;
SELECT system_name, description FROM AI_Systems WHERE system_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Network_Operations ORDER BY operation_type DESC;
SELECT operation_type, operation_status FROM Network_Operations WHERE operation_id = 5;
SELECT service_name FROM 5G_Service_Quality WHERE service_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems WHERE system_id = 1;
SELECT system_name, description FROM AI_Systems WHERE system_id > 3;
SELECT * FROM AI_Systems JOIN Network_Operations ON AI_Systems.system_id = Network_Operations.operation_id;
SELECT system_name, operation_status, service_description FROM AI_Systems, Network_Operations, 5g_service_quality WHERE system_id = 2 AND operation_id = 1;
SELECT DISTINCT system_id, service_name FROM 5g_service_quality WHERE service_description LIKE '%5G%' AND service_id < 5;
SELECT * FROM network_devices;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM network_devices WHERE device_type = 'router';
SELECT device_name, location FROM network_devices ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT operation_name, started_at, completed_at FROM network_operations WHERE completed_at > '2022-01-01';
SELECT model_name, trained_on, accuracy FROM ai_models WHERE accuracy >= 90.00;
SELECT * FROM network_devices ORDER BY device_name DESC;
SELECT device_name, device_type, location FROM network_devices WHERE device_type = 'Router';
SELECT device_name, firmware_version FROM network_devices WHERE location LIKE '%Floor%' ORDER BY device_name ASC;
SELECT operation_name, operation_type, started_at, completed_at FROM network_operations WHERE operation_type IN ('Configuration', 'Upgrade');
SELECT model_name, model_type, trained_on, accuracy FROM ai_models WHERE accuracy > 90 ORDER BY trained_on DESC;
SELECT * FROM network_devices;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM network_devices WHERE device_status = TRUE;
SELECT device_id, device_name, device_location FROM network_devices ORDER BY device_location DESC;
SELECT * FROM network_users WHERE user_role = 'admin';
SELECT model_name, model_accuracy FROM ai_models WHERE model_accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM network_devices;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM network_devices WHERE device_status = TRUE;
SELECT user_name, user_email, user_role FROM network_users ORDER BY user_name ASC;
SELECT model_name, model_accuracy FROM ai_models WHERE model_accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT prediction_data FROM ai_predictions WHERE prediction_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY prediction_timestamp DESC;
